## Content & Imagery

Sample artisan profiles, product stories and testimonials in this repository
are illustrative and have been written for demonstration purposes. Where the
names of crafts, regions and traditions appear (Jaipur Blue Pottery, Banarasi
weaving, Madhubani painting, Dhokra metalwork, Pashmina, Pattachitra,
Channapatna, Kantha, Bidriware, Meenakari, etc.), the cultural rights and
heritage belong to the artisan communities of India and are used here with
deep respect.

Stock photography is sourced from Unsplash and used under the
[Unsplash License](https://unsplash.com/license).

If you intend to deploy this project commercially, please replace the sample
data with content licensed directly from the artisans whose work you list.
